asset.description:
See how easy it is to add more performance to the 2009-2013 Chevy Corvette ZR-1 6.2L.

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=63-3080

K&N 63-3080 air intake modification showed an estimated gain of 27 horsepower at 5948 RPM when tested on the K&N dynamometer. 

K&N 63-3080 fits the following: 
2013 CHEVROLET CORVETTE ZR-1 6.2L V8 
2012 CHEVROLET CORVETTE ZR-1 6.2L V8 
2011 CHEVROLET CORVETTE ZR-1 6.2L V8
2010 CHEVROLET CORVETTE ZR-1 6.2L V8 
2009 CHEVROLET CORVETTE ZR-1 6.2L V8 
 
Go to http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=63-3080 for an up to date application list.
